### MamaCare REST API Comprehensive Tests
# To use in Postman: You can copy the JSON blocks directly into the raw Body of your Postman requests.
# Or use the VS Code "REST Client" extension to click "Send Request" right here!

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@phone_number = +2348012345678
@admin_token = your_admin_jwt_here
@patient_token = your_patient_jwt_here
@doctor_token = your_doctor_jwt_here

### =======================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION
### =======================================

### 1a. Patient Signup (Request OTP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/patient/otp/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "+2347048413823"
}

### 1b. Patient Signup (Verify OTP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/patient/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
 "pin_id": "d2c1456b-5fbd-4080-ba48-2819bbfd4906",
  "code":"798978"
  
}

### 1c. Doctor Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/doctor/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dr.adaeze@ubth.ng",
  "password": "mamacare123"
}

### =======================================
### 2. PATIENT PROFILE & INTAKE
### =======================================

### 2a. Get Current Patient Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients/me
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

### 2b. Add Pregnancy Record
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients/pregnancy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

{
  "lmp_date": "2023-10-01T00:00:00Z",
  "blood_group": "O+",
  "genotype": "AA",
  "booking_weight": 65.5,
  "booking_height": 165
}

### 2c. Submit Medical Intake Form (Biodata, Obstetric, etc.)
POST {{baseUrl}}/intake
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

{
  "domain": "biodata",
  "question_key": "marital_status",
  "answer": "Married"
}

### =======================================
### 3. RISK ASSESSMENT & SYMPTOMS
### =======================================

### 3a. Trigger Risk Assessment (AI evaluates patient risk)
POST {{baseUrl}}/risk/assess
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

{
  "patient_id": "REPLACE_WITH_PATIENT_ID"
}

### 3b. Log Symptoms (Triggers Danger Pipeline & WhatsApp Alerts)
POST {{baseUrl}}/symptoms
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: unique-random-string-123
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

{
  "symptoms": [
    {
      "symptom_key": "vaginal_bleeding",
      "severity": "moderate",
      "notes": "Started this morning"
    }
  ]
}

### 3c. Get Patient Symptom Timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients/REPLACE_WITH_PATIENT_ID/symptoms
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

### =======================================
### 4. DOCTOR ALERTS
### =======================================

### 4a. Get Active Danger Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=open
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

### 4b. Acknowledge Alert (Doctor claims it)
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts/REPLACE_WITH_ALERT_ID/acknowledge
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

### =======================================
### 5. APPOINTMENTS
### =======================================

### 5a. Book Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: unique-random-string-456
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

{
  "doctor_id": "REPLACE_WITH_DOCTOR_ID",
  "slot_start": "2024-11-20T10:00:00Z"
}

### 5b. Get Appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments?status=booked
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

### =======================================
### 6. AI EDUCATION & PROVIDERS
### =======================================

### 6a. Get Education Modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/education/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

### 6b. Search Nearby Hospitals
GET {{baseUrl}}/providers/nearby?lat=6.5244&lng=3.3792&radius=10
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

### =======================================
### 7. ADMIN (DEPARTMENT HEAD)
### =======================================

### 7a. Assign Doctor to Patient (Triggers SMS to patient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/patients/REPLACE_WITH_PATIENT_ID/assign-doctor
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "doctor_id": "REPLACE_WITH_DOCTOR_ID"
}

### 7b. Get Hospital Risk Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/risk-overview
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
